Juicy & Tender Filipino BBQ Skewers!

Do you prefer Chicken or Pork?! 🐓🐷

📍Grill City inside Seafood City at Southcenter Mall.

Check out my previous post and enter my $1,000 gift card giveaway! 🙌👍

node.text:
$1,000 Shopping Spree🛍🍴✨Westfield Southcenter is making back to school season even better with their Back-To-School Double Rewards campaign, and in celebration we’re giving away a $1,000 gift card to one lucky winner!

To Enter: 
1. Follow @westfieldsouthcenter + @seattlefoodieadventure
2. Tag a friend below who you’re going back to school shopping with.

Head down to #WestfieldSC and use your gift card to shop at retailers like Footlocker, Abercrombie & Fitch, Lucky Brand & more, or dine at some of our favorite restaurants like Din Tai Fung, The Cheesecake Factory and Jollibee. 
-- Giveaway not affiliated with IG. Winners will be contacted by @seattlefoodieadventure. NoPurNec. Open only to legal U.S. residents residing in WA, 18+. Ends 08/26/21 at 11:59 PM PST. Rules: https://bit.ly/3818Qae

node.text:
Check out these beignets from @jet_city_beignet! It was so delicious and yummy! You can dip, spread, and eat it with or without the sauces. They have a pop-up this Saturday in Tacoma at the Metropolitan Market from 9am - 1pm. Stop by and show some love! 

TAG your friends below ⬇, Double Tap if you love beignets!!! 🏃‍♂️🏃‍♀️🙌
.
.

node.text:
Hands down the best spicy fried chicken sandwich! No bs. The chicken was very crispy on the outside and super juicy inside. The portion size is gigantic and the spices is unlike I’ve ever had! Are you a fan?!

Stop by @yummymeatsanddeli and get yours today! 509 S 3rd St, Renton. 

TAG your friends and comment below ⬇️ for questions! 🔥🙌
.
.
.
.
.

node.text:
CLOSED!! Congrats @susannee.c, @amanda_walia, and @knsaechao!🚨GIVEAWAY! I'm teaming up with @SeattleCidCelebration to give away $40 gift cards to 3 lucky winners! 2 winners will receive a $20 GC each to Dim Sum King & Tai Tung, and 1 winner will win $20 GC to Jade Garden & Honey Court! 

As many of you are aware, Seattle Chinatown International District has been impacted by Covid and Asian hate crimes, resulting in an economic downturn for many restaurants and mom-and-pop shops. As part of our effort to revitalize Chinatown, we are inviting you to come join us for a fun day of multicultural entertainment, activities for kids and family, and more! There will be raffle drawing every hour, giving away a total of $4,000 worth of local restaurants and amazon gift cards! SWIPE ⬅️ to see the official flyer and look below ⬇️ for how TO ENTER! I hope to see y’all there! #sponsored 

1️⃣. LIKE this photo. 
2️⃣. FOLLOW @SeattleCidCelebration + @SeattleFoodieAdventure 
3️⃣. TAG your friends! Multiple entries allowed and encouraged!
4️⃣. Repost this post to your story for additional 10 entries! Please DM me a screenshot if your acct is private. 🙌
5️⃣. 3 lucky winners will be randomly selected on August 5th at 5pm. Announcing winners via story after 7pm.
.
.
.

What are your weekend plans for brunch?! Stop by @derumarket! They’re finally open now for dine-in, so make sure to make a reservation online before showing up! Also don’t sleep on their fried chicken & gravy! Hands down one of the best I’ve ever had! SWIPE ⬅️ to see the lemongrass tea & donut and check out my story for the total bill. TAG your friends below ⬇, Double Tap if you love Brunch!!! 🏃‍♂️🏃‍♀️

node.text:
Hey gang! I’m finally on TikTok! Feel free to find me by searching for @SeattleFoodieAdventure - I recently upgraded my camera so expect to see more🔥content and delicious Seattle eats! I appreciate your loyal support and thank you for supporting local restaurants! 😘❤️

This is from @thecottagebothell at 
10029 NE 183rd St, Bothell, WA 98011. 
I highly recommend stopping by for brunch! This is the perfect spot to bring your family and friends! I’ll have to stop by again and get their big pitcher of mimosas, lol. 

Comment below ⬇️ if you have any questions! 🥰🙌
.

node.text:
Biscuits and marionberry jam from @halfandhalfdoughnuts. As weird as it sounds, this donut shop got the best biscuits in town! Make sure to microwave for about 20 seconds and it will taste like fresh straight from the oven. I also got the strawberry donut! Swipe ⬅️. It was enormous and very delicious! The frosting literally melted in my mouth….so good! 🍩🍓I’ll have to come back and try their cronuts…

TAG your friends ⬇️ and drag them with you to Half and Half Doughnuts! 🏃‍♀️🏃‍♂️🙌
.
.
.
.
.
.
